1. **Neverovatan** prizor se odvijao ispred nas. (An incredible sight was unfolding in front of us.)
2. Nisam **neverovatno** dobar u matematici. (I'm not incredibly good at math.)
3. Taj film je bio **neverovatan**! (That movie was amazing!)
4. Ona ima **neverovatne** sposobnosti. (She has incredible abilities.)
5. Bio sam **neverovatno** umoran posle dugog puta. (I was incredibly tired after a long journey.)
6. Njegova izdržljivost je **neverovatna**. (His endurance is incredible.)
7. **Neverovatan** je osećaj kada uspete u nečemu teškom. (It's an incredible feeling when you succeed in something difficult.)
8. Ova knjiga mi je donela **neverovatnu** inspiraciju. (This book brought me incredible inspiration.)
9. Ona je napravila **neverovatan** kolač za rođendan. (She made an incredible cake for the birthday.)
10. **Neverovatno** je kako se svet menja. (It's incredible how the world is changing.)